      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">9.108-4</ph> Waiver.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d566e8" class="- topic/p ">Any agency head may waive the prohibition in subsection <xref href="9.108-2.dita#FAR_9_108_2"
                  base="i1116407"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">9.108-2</xref> and the requirement of subsection <xref href="9.108-3.dita#FAR_9_108_3"
                  base="i1116415"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">9.108-3</xref> for a specific contract if the agency head determines in writing that the waiver is required in the interest of national security, documents the determination, and reports it to the Congress.</p>
      </conbody>
